{"tid":293372,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"山本寬(叔)：和差點解僱我的京都(動畫)，不是其他動畫公司能比","createTime":"2017-06-22T06:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T12:45:56.000Z","uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14e08ba01ef3865c05d66f446b1157f1c0552c00","tid":293372,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"作為參考的涼宮春日的『God knows』驚人到要我差點昏過去。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;WUG的『Beyond the Bottom』能製作成那樣，真的不得不感謝京都動畫啊。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;『God knows』之後還有首『Lost my music』，雖然演奏畫面只有一點點。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我當時要是『涼宮春日』的監督的話，肯定會把這話的叫山本什麼寬的31歲臭小鬼演出給解雇了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;不過當時我確實處在被解僱的邊緣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;可見當時的京都動畫有多厲害，不是其他連名字我都不想說的動畫公司能比的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nライブアライブ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017/6/21 22:48<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遂にコンテが大メインクライマックスの、最後の演奏シーンに差し掛かり、あれ？どこまでやればいいんだ？と思って、参考までに『God knows...』の尺を計ってみる。<br />\n2分38秒・・・。<br />\n鬼やわ・・・。<br />\nカット数では49。<br />\nここで一旦、気を失いかける。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因みに『Beyond the Bottom』の時は、ネクストストーム10カット、I-110カット、WUG20カット、計40カットと決めていた。<br />\nそれ以上は制作上無理だったからだ。<br />\n<br />\nそれをあれだけ濃密なTVシリーズで超えてたんだね・・・。<br />\n本当、京アニには感謝しかないわ・・・。<br />\n<br />\nこの後に更に（演奏シーンはちょっとだけど）『Lost my music』があったんだからね。<br />\n俺が『ハルヒ』の監督だったら、この話数の山本ナントカっていう当時31歳の若造演出は、クビにするね。<br />\nまぁ実際その瀬戸際まで行ったんだけど。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nそれだけ（当時の）京アニが凄かったというのと、それだけ他のスタジオがクソゴミだったということを、ここで強調しておきたい。<br />\n具体的に会社名は挙げないけど。推して知るべし。"},{"pid":"8c4adf958de6da0664f40734ef9980047329d51a","tid":293372,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"05b016a238a4124a081be79b11789a065d4b077b","tid":293372,"uid":25028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T06:59:59.000Z","msg":"up乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a15a6d0b8690897cf3bcd20d97bbd8913c20f3","tid":293372,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:00:01.000Z","msg":"乜撚野啊"},{"pid":"1cc59b0c2356166dc50175675be67e4909b0c4bf","tid":293372,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"井語學日文舊制N1版"},{"pid":"55f8688de5d10efc68baf9cc6a8f2bd3aa402905","tid":293372,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"今次我都睇唔明阿台主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051bdd1a3dad9c2efce04003355ec88a5f15b120","tid":293372,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次我都睇唔明阿台主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n贊京都動畫回億以前制作動畫時既事"},{"pid":"961f5e2bb065fa9fe6234ad5da7be9e501fd7d2c","tid":293372,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"樓上串9台主班人全部比我make低哂"},{"pid":"4584ff8577b52e5acc62470bd26eff33abd55252","tid":293372,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"又屈"},{"pid":"6f92664e7759e78dc6ca91a68b63edd1ae6e763a","tid":293372,"uid":39413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"如果當年中文閲讀卷出呢篇野我實u撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9f6f0f2e0de51929b143a5bf136b45cb3ed3b6","tid":293372,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d07a621909a9eb0f60d5111c8cc0638377d9d10","tid":293372,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n(叔)"},{"pid":"98b8b4bdab76a945502e44ec317279e230cb63bc","tid":293372,"uid":53979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl